                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4811,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_7086984801760748.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Khaenri'ah",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dainsleif was the Twilight Sword and the former captain of the Khaenri'ahn Royal Guard.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_5671433247808590288.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Khaenri'ahn cataclysm",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "During the cataclysm, Dainsleif was cursed with immortality by Celestia. He was one of the six people who should have prevented the disaster and stopped the Vinster King from continuing to rock the foundation of the world. His main goal is to stop the Abyss Order.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Traveler's Sibling",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Traveler's sibling and the Princess/Prince of the Abyss Order, who used to be Dainsleif's companion.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7484,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/19/237301566/0de0f341fb6d635a244abdc184e5ebb7_2860191000081268700.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Vedrfolnir",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "One of the five Khaenri'ahn Sinners and Dainsleif's older brother.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2467,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/npc/Halfdan_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Halfdan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "One of the royal guards under Dainsleif's command.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
