                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Teyvat Chapter Storyline Preview: Travail",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/10/237301566/38416655ede42df809629ff677bb17be_5064298490952837940.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "September 28, 2020",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Version 2.6 \"Zephyr of the Violet Garden\" Trailer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/10/237301566/6d179f9c1e87c9add5dd8dc9a5ad0ffe_8112163713542439007.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "March 18, 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "A vast wind breezes across the fields and encounters the illustrious poetry and pictures of the violet garden.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The pure light of a deep, secluded valley illuminates a corner of the dark abyss.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "On the surface of the reflective water, stories of the past are gradually emerging...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Version 3.5 \"Windblume's Breath\" Trailer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/22/237301566/9b6ccdb41e742840308daac5efb843c3_2895616554537489816.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "February 17, 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Some say fate hides in the wind, like the fragrance of flowers, like rain and dew...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Such is the law of nature, absolute and insurmountable.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Others, on the other hand, strive to seek out their own destinies, or even go as far as to reweave the threads of fate.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "But at the end of it all, is this not an orchestration of fate?",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Version 4.7 \"An Everlasting Dream Intertwined\" Trailer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/06/237301566/9b42d35f9a503427ac6a0d50d08badc2_6712732388128120438.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "May 24, 2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "People often feel trapped by the past.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "All those unresolved regrets,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "And all those unanswered questions.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Perhaps there'll come a day when they'll be set right,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Or maybe they'll just keep playing out in your dreams.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Illustrations and Emojis",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Paimon's Paintings 33",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/20/237301566/87c235718b9047566f2a1411709c8b82_1866882249866373092.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "June 12, 2024",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Greetings, Travelers! The latest emojis from Genshin Impact are now available on HoYoLAB~",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Paimon's Paintings include a collection of chibi emojis of various Genshin Impact characters. We hope you like them! Paimon will continue to paint more cute emojis for everyone~",
